com.pstmetro.generics

Class NodeLinkedList<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pstmetro.generics.NodeLinkedList<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of Object you wish to store within the code
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<V>, Collection<V>, List<V>

    public class NodeLinkedList<V>
extends Object
implements List<V>
    The ArraySet class is merely a custom implementation of a LinkedList and, is created by starting from a head node and moving along to the element desired. We created this class to prove that we are able to create efficient Data structures. This list could be improved by doubly linking and using a tail, we deemed it unnecessary for the required project as it is used in only one case.s
